Package: EPScraper
Title: Scrapers For EliteProspects
Version: 0.0.0.9002
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Palmeri", email = "matthewpalmeri@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package contains functions useful for scrapping information off of the website
    eliteprospects.com. Included in this are functions to gather information for an individual player,
    an individual goalie, as well as functions to grab all the information from a draft or league stats
    page (as well as helper functions).
Depends: R (>= 3.5.3)
Imports: 
    dplyr (>= 0.8.0.1),
    lubridate (>= 1.7.4),
    magrittr (>= 1.5),
    rvest (>= 0.3.2),
    stringi (>= 1.4.3),
    stringr (>= 1.4.0),
    tidyr (>= 0.8.3),
    XML (>= 3.98-1.19)
